reviews.text: About 200 events per year! Creative industries place. Rock, rap, rave, jungle, dnb, classical and other music. Sports, wedings are happening here. In the summer in back yard are big terrace. Food is tasty. Staff is friendly and pros. Loftas is working more than 10year

A great place to visit. Vilnius becoming one of many the street art cities and this place gives a space for artists to express their ideas. Its and open air exhibition which is worth seeing together with a guide! You will find light instalations, stencil art, and even more. Dont miss a chance to visit the place while being in Vilnius!

Update: some pieces of art have gone but some new appeared. Also new climbing places have been opened here, so place becoming as art and activities hub.
Very nice venue with everything you might need inside.

A little too hot (with full house), sound leaves you wishing for just that little bit more (troubles with clarity in mid range (vocals, synthesizers)). In my humble opinion stage is a bit too high, makes too much separation between public and artists.

venue was dissapointing. the sound was not great and had multiple issues through the concert. i was surprised how many kids were working by the coats (by working i mean just existing there and talking with each other, while people are standing in line). paying to leave the coat gave a nasty vibe. also no soap or paper towels in the bathroom
